author: stefan2
msg: Slightly improve scalability and performance of the temp serializer.
Instead of creating a new stack element for each new (sibbling)
structure, recycle the stack elements after usage and reuse them

author: stefan2
msg: Re-implement svn_io_read_length_line as this is one of the
most-called functions in SVN. Instead of reading data a byte
at a time, read 128 byte chunks and scan those.

author: aharui
msg: A few tests were still not using embedded fonts.  Hopefully they now are.
